data.description: Beautiful single-story Home in the quiet neighborhood of Alderon Woods, The Woodlands. This upgraded townhouse features wood flooring in the living room & dining room, carpets in bedrooms and tile in bathrooms. Open layout. Formal Dining Room with bay window, Living Room with stone fireplace. Kitchen has Corian Countertops and Stainless-Steel appliances with a breakfast nook and breakfast bar. Also, a study with built-in desk that can be converted into a 3rd bedroom because it has a Murphy bed. A large master bedroom with vaulted ceiling and large windows open to the backyard area, Bathroom with tub and separate shower, double vanities, walk in closet and plenty of storage. Large second bedroom. Second bathroom with tub/shower. Private backyard completely fenced with deck that backs to greenbelt. Two car garage. Washer, dryer and refrigerator included. Easy access to 242 and I-45. Conroe ISD Schools.
